 	Key bindings
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

  arrows Change view angle
  0      Reset view angle
  ESC    Exit




This took about 5 hours including the time it took to re-watch parts of Thursdays lecture.




